data.description: Just completed major addition and renovation! Charming original and new merged with state of the art design, technology and  stylish material.  Over-the top new gourmet kitchen bringing together form and functions will be the heart of the home for family and friends. A few of the beautiful details include rare Brazilian Quartzite counters, GE Cafe Series appliances w/three ovens, great wet bar/butler's pantry, large walk-in pantry, Anderson Low-E Glass windows, custom cabinets and custom-built range hood. Kitchen is open to the dining and living rooms. Dining flows onto welcoming porch for easy entertaining. Main level also has new laundry room and standout full bath. Amazing new primary suite addition features stunning bath with copper soaking tub, private balcony with water views and a spiral staircase to the office/loft and an oversized walk-in closet. The new top level's loft/office area with windows on 3 sides with be a favorite place to work and relax and can be entered through the primary suite or the 2nd floor hall.  Lower level's main highlight is a suite with two new bedrooms, a full bath and a family room area.  A 2nd laundry area and garage is accessible from this level as well.  All baths are renovated and finished with stone and tile. Extra attention was paid to the homes infrastructure to ensure smart water management/water proofing, insulation, sound proofing, and home is tech forward and ready. Major bonus upgrades include custom Rustica doors, metal standing seam roof, state of the art hot water, great heating and cooling systems and new retaining wall. Alley in the back of the house provides convenient access to private parking and also leads to water access for kayaks directly across the street.  275 Smith is a few blocks to multiple restaurants, entertainment, water access and public trails.  Walk to Downtown Annapolis or hop on the free shuttle or water taxi!
